I find the thought of this theory being unbelievable quite funny, seeing as how many deluded fans are making theories of Ashara Dayne being Jon’s mother despite all the evidence shoved in their faces that it’s Lyanna, and yet a vague theory like this one (which makes sense with Bloodravens character) is denied so quickly. 

